  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a claypot over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped nuka-pickle and cook for 2 minutes, until slightly caramelized.",
    "Add the tagliatelle, soy sauce, vinegar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 10 minutes, until the tagliatelle is al dente.",
    "Remove the claypot from the heat and let it rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the Lomo Saltado hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
